fu.obj

Class SmallestN<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fu.obj.SmallestN<T>

  • public class SmallestN<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Queue that detects the smallest n elements. Important: if two elements are equal (from the viewpoint of compareTo) only one is stored, i.e. this container has the characteristic of a set.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors

      Generate a queue that holds up to n smallest elements.
